The paper discusses the use of deep learning approaches for improving the perception of endoscopic capsule robots, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The use of visual and magnetic sensors also suggests that computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE) techniques may be employed.
